Paul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 01:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-create-supercharged-vitamin-k-that-helps-the-brain-heal-itself</guid></item><item><title>光物质粒子可能永远改变人工智能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/light-matter-particles-could-change-ai-forever</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 01:16:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/light-matter-particles-could-change-ai-forever</guid></item><item><title>科学家创造出第一个可以交流的人工神经元</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-create-the-first-artificial-neuron-that-can-communicate</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 01:01:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-create-the-first-artificial-neuron-that-can-communicate</guid></item><item><title>如何让大脑理论重获新生</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/how-to-breathe-life-back-into-brain-theory</link><description>神经科学需要停止将大脑视为一台计算机。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-to-breathe-life-back-into-brain-theory2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/how-to-breathe-life-back-into-brain-theory</guid></item><item><title>奈杰尔·阿克兰：平凡……非凡——仿生手臂的生活</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/nigel-ackland-ordinaryextraordinary-life-with-a-bionic-arm</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nigel-ackland-ordinaryextraordinary-life-with-a-bionic-arm.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/nigel-ackland-ordinaryextraordinary-life-with-a-bionic-arm</guid></item><it